      text04 : {
        val : '<section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><p style="text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="" src="http://39.96.80.148:8085/news/list04.jpg"/></p></section></section><section><section><section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">政务礼仪是国家公务机关及相关事业单位在内部沟通交流及对外服务，与社会接触时的礼仪。5月27日晚，由三月雨组织开展的政务礼仪沙龙正式拉开帷幕。前来接受讲解员培训的全国各地的文化传播者、国家级解说员、讲解员代表等出席了本次活动。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section></section></section><section><section><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="" src="http://39.96.80.148:8085/news/list06.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p></section></section><section><section><section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">课程结合晚宴，从言谈举止、服饰、用餐礼节等方面，引领学员了解并掌握政务礼仪的相关知识。宴会中，集团特邀多次获得全国国标舞大赛冠军的Ken老师带领大家领略华尔兹艺术，并以亲身展示的视觉盛宴完美的为本期政务沙龙活动画上句号。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><section><section></section></section><section><section><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="" src="http://39.96.80.148:8085/news/list07.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p></section></section><section><section><section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">作为新时代的讲解员，不仅要具备基本的礼仪常识，更应该具备深厚的文化修养，学习并掌握政务礼仪为新时代讲解员的发展拓宽了道路。三月雨讲解员培训班愿秉持匠心培养新面貌、高素养、符合时代要求的一名又一名文化传播者。为社会注入新的能量，助力实现“用文化提升国家软实力”的伟大目标。</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p></section>',
        title : '三月雨开展政务礼仪沙龙活动',
        date : ' 2019-05-29'
