      text05 : {
        val : '<section><section><section><section><section><section><section><p style="text-align: center;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><video src="http://39.96.80.148/jspx/video/01.mp4" controls="controls" width="850" height="478">您的浏览器不支持 video 标签。</video></p></section><section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">2019年6月25日，为期四天的讲解员培训班在三月雨四知堂报告厅圆满落幕。来自上海、河南、山东、青岛等全国各地的文化传播者、国家级解说员、讲解员代表等共14个单位的31名学员参加了结业考核并获得结业证书。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section></section><section><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="" src="http://39.96.80.148:8085/news/05-1.jpg" width="824" height="710"/></p><p><br/></p></section><section><section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">本期的培训班共进行了11个专题课程的学习，分别为《中国文化传播》、《从胜利走向胜利》、《展厅接待与礼仪综合素养》、《讲解员技能专项训练与实战教学》、《政务礼仪沙龙》、《博物院与讲解》、《讲解漫谈》、《中华传统文化雅集》、《模拟讲解实战练习》、《观摩国家级讲解员风采》、《艺术欣赏》。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section></section><section><section><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="" src="http://39.96.80.148:8085/news/05-2.jpg" width="751" height="558"/></p></section></section><section><section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">作为新时代的讲解员，我们不仅需要不断提高理论水平，进一步丰富和充实知识量和文化素养，更需要具有终身学习的意识和独立深入思考的能力。三月雨讲解员培训班以一月一期一相聚的授课模式，以正确的理论引导人，以正能量鼓舞人，以正义道德感染人，以时代精神带动人，愿大家带着满满的收获，在传播先进文化和弘扬时代精神的道路上携手奋进，砥砺前行。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section></section><section><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="" src="http://39.96.80.148:8085/news/05-3.jpg" width="735" height="575"/></p><p><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section><section><section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">学员心得感悟节选</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section></section><section><section><section><section><section></section><section></section><section></section></section><section><section><section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">平顶山市纪委&nbsp;杨蕾</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">这是一次难忘而又深刻的“充电学习”，说的真诚一点，这是一次对我极有意义的“思想之旅”。原来的我对讲解员的印象仅停留在自己作为观众去展厅了解的那一点凤毛麟角。对于即将要上岗成为一名讲解员也安之若素，并不觉得这对于播音主持专业的我有什么压力。但四天的学习如同打开另一个世界的一扇门：“呀，讲解员的天地如此广阔。”</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><br/></span></p></section></section><section><section><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="" src="http://39.96.80.148:8085/n