style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">上海龙华烈士纪念馆&nbsp;翁怡</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">作为一个刚刚迈入讲解员行列的新人，我仿佛受到了一次由内而外的洗礼。那些生动真实的红色故事，那些有血有肉的人物让我有了更深刻的认识：信仰确实存在力量，确实曾有许多人为之奋斗，仍有许多人在为之奋斗，更值得我们新一代中国人为之奋斗。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section></section><section><section><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="" src="http://39.96.80.148:8085/news/05-6.jpg" width="719" height="550"/></p></section><section><br/></section></section><section><section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">徐州公安局 孙一男</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">严厉又慈祥的于老师带给我们很多专业内容和感动，她身上那份对于讲解事业的热爱深深地影响着我，她为了工作的那份忘我精神，值得我一生学习。她深情的演讲常常感动着我们也感动着自己，这种由心而发的感情，是打动听者最重要的内涵。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">卢勇老师作为国防大学的教授，丝毫没有带给我们距离感，相反，他上课常常用我们的名字讲故事，生动又幽默。卢勇老师温文尔雅，娓娓道来，很有知识分子的儒雅气质。他用深厚的历史功底，深入浅出地为我们讲解着党的历史，使我受益匪浅。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section></section><section><section><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="" src="http://39.96.80.148:8085/news/05-7.jpg" width="805" height="1112"/></p></section></section><section><section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section></section><section><section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 0em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: brea